ces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去醫院驗傷時勁後悔，因為個癲佬留案底<br />\n用摔都可以，總之唔好出手打佢為上策<br />\n屌佢，推佢，摔佢，引佢追，呢D都可以安全地玩到佢儍，總之千萬唔好出手打佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鄧你唔抵，有冇後悔打得唔夠狼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實講佢已經好傷<br />\n再傷D 可能我會更重罪，唔係公眾地方打架而係傷人了"},{"pid":"8c5d6ca25dc2fdd6e99a34c6c2f6d482b014fae5","tid":44104,"uid":45170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"我degree架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62c4d2d886879d1775e7e3f1030bc5b98c98023","tid":44104,"uid":61510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁咪打鳩佢囉 驚佢識醉拳呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係驚唔夠佢打  但大街大行 好多CCTV影住  唔想上身可以點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打說了重點出來！如果唔到危險關頭，同廢老打，唔小心打傷左廢老，廢老就變左受害者，而自衛者就因為個廢老而犯左刑事，香港犯左刑事等同收皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da891fe6276c09c30db2abdb83729f71f0dd6ba5","tid":44104,"uid":27447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁咪打鳩佢囉 驚佢識醉拳呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係驚唔夠佢打  但大街大行 好多CCTV影住  唔想上身可以點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打說了重點出來！如果唔到危險關頭，同廢老打，唔小心打傷左廢老，廢老就變左受害者，而自衛者就因為個廢老而犯左刑事，香港犯左刑事等同收皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯  到時佢咁傷 係黑警面前死狗咁屈我打鳩佢先 咁咪好撚無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係後行 無CCTV 無人睇到就話遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大街應該要有其他應對方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4eacfa85ac23ca0368c7a5bafdc5f57b57886b6","tid":44104,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"一膽二力三功夫 撲低佢打地戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2af4dba89e22f8b787021242df7f664dd5143e","tid":44104,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:23:43.000Z","msg":"一拳轟落去"},{"pid":"d11f74ab5d7f9b9db30f2142a1dcfd67cb4c6070","tid":44104,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f27df9a77fdcbd1707c7bb166f3ea78b9923e24","tid":44104,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"用太極<br />\n<br />\n佢撲埋黎 你一個閃身避開<br />\n順手用力幫佢加速 將佢帶落地下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b720c1951f6c065f0dad35137d3a8133e0bf1df","tid":44104,"uid":61510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係驚唔夠佢打  但大街大行 好多CCTV影住  唔想上身可以點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打說了重點出來！如果唔到危險關頭，同廢老打，唔小心打傷左廢老，廢老就變左受害者，而自衛者就因為個廢老而犯左刑事，香港犯左刑事等同收皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯  到時佢咁傷 係黑警面前死狗咁屈我打鳩佢先 咁咪好撚無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係後行 無CCTV 無人睇到就話遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大街應該要有其他應對方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暫時最好方法係一邊走一邊小條友，再按你良心，睇你會唔會引佢出馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9cb7011bb92f515b92c06394161d156030b1d1","tid":44104,"uid":27447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T18:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一膽二力三功夫 撲低佢打地戰<img src=\"/as